Name:		xmms-input-smpeg
Version:	0.3.5
Release:	3
License:	GPL
Group:		X11/Applications/Multimedia
Source0:	http://www.xmms.org/files/plugins/smpeg-xmms/smpeg-xmms-%{version}.tar.gz
